rioja Change Log

Version 0.5-4

	* Released on CRAN 27/10/09

	Fixed bug in WAPLS CPP & R code that crashed R with PLS 
	(identified by Richard Telford) 
	
	Fixed bug in WAPLS R code that incorrectly calculated predicted 
	values with standx=TRUE 
	
	Fixed bug in help file (WA example) pointed out by Sven Adler

Version 0.5-3

	* Released on CRAN, 12/8/09
	
  Fixed bug in analog.c that crashed on 64 bit compilations.
	
  Replaced RODBC calls on non-Windows platforms with calls to 
  read.xls in package gdata

  Removed call to malloc.h that prevented compilation on MacSO X
  
  Added function sp.plot
  
  

Version 0.5-2

	* First Release on CRAN, 6/8/09
